<section class="bg-[var(--color-bg)]">
    <div class="mx-auto w-[92%] sm:w-[90%] md:w-[88%] lg:w-[85%] py-12 md:py-16">
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[var(--color-text)]">International Exchange Policy</h1>
        <p class="mt-3 text-[var(--color-muted)] max-w-2xl">Need to swap a product for a different size, color, or model? Here's how exchanges work for international orders.</p>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
            <div class="rounded-[var(--radius-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-6">
                <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-4">How international exchanges work</h2>
                <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">Due to the complexity of international shipping and customs, we handle exchanges as a <strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">return + new order</strong> process:</p>
                <ol class="space-y-3 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] list-decimal list-inside">
                    <li><a href="/contact" class="text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:underline">Contact us</a> within 30 days of delivery to request the exchange.</li>
                    <li>We initiate a return for the original item and provide shipping instructions.</li>
                    <li>Once the return is confirmed (shipped or received), we create a new order for the replacement.</li>
                    <li>The replacement ships as a fresh order with full tracking.</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-6">
                <div class="rounded-[var(--radius-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-6">
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-3">Shipping costs</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-emerald-500">&#10003;</span> <strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Defective item:</strong> We cover return shipping and ship the replacement free of charge.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">&#8226;</span> <strong class="text-[var(--color-text)]">Change of mind:</strong> Return shipping is at your expense. Standard shipping rates apply to the replacement order (free shipping thresholds still apply).</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="rounded-[var(--radius-card)] border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] p-6">
                    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-[var(--color-text)] mb-3">Customs duties on exchanges</h2>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">&#8226;</span> The replacement order is a new shipment and may incur duties in DAP countries.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">&#8226;</span> For defective exchanges, we'll mark the package as a warranty replacement to help minimize duties.</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">&#8226;</span> You can reclaim duties on the returned item through your country's customs office.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a href="/international-returns" class="inline-flex h-10 items-center rounded-[var(--radius-button)] border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] px-5 text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] transition hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">International Returns</a>
            <a href="/customs-duties" class="inline-flex h-10 items-center rounded-[var(--radius-button)] border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-surface)] px-5 text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-text)] transition hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] hover:text-[var(--color-accent)]">Customs & Duties FAQ</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-[var(--radius-button)] bg-[var(--color-accent)] px-5 text-sm font-semibold text-white transition hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-hover)]">
                Start an Exchange
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
